result: .content {	width: 95%;	margin: 0 auto;}.explain-title {	margin: 21.5px 0;	p {		font-size: 17px;		color: #333333;	}}.explain-img {	width: 100%;	margin: 0 auto;	img {		width: 100%;		height: 151.5px;	}}.explain-tip {	p {		font-size: 13px;		color: #000000;		opacity: 0.8;	}}.explain-btn {	width: 100%;	margin: 36px auto;	p {		width: 311px;		height: 48px;		background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #f7bc61 0%, #ffe3a0 100%), linear-gradient(#323232, #323232);		background-blend-mode: normal, normal;		border-radius: 24px;		margin: 0 auto;		text-align: center;		line-height: 48px;		font-size: 17px;		color: #64442e;	}}
